768
00:46:04.427 --> 00:46:05.428
Aku hanya gugup.

769
00:46:07.221 --> 00:46:08.473
Tidak perlu gugup.

770
00:46:09.932 --> 00:46:10.933
Jangan mengacau.

771
00:46:11.350 --> 00:46:12.393
